<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<main>
    <section class="hero-section about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6 text-md-left">
                    <h1>WHO WE ARE</h1>
                    <p>
                        Welcome to <strong>Shoezie</strong> — your destination for bold steps and bold styles. Born out of a passion for shoes and a drive to redefine comfort, we combine fashion-forward design with everyday wearability.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Whether you're chasing trends or walking your own path, Shoezie is here to support every step.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                    <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Team Shoezie" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 350px;">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="new-arrivals about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>OUR MISSION</h2>
            <p class="text-center" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                At Shoezie, we’re driven by one simple mission: <strong>To make shoes that feel as good as they look</strong>. We obsess over quality materials, comfort-fit technology, and bold aesthetics — so you never have to choose between style and comfort.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="top-selling about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 40px;">WHAT MAKES SHOEZIE DIFFERENT?</h2>
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4">  
                    <img src="/images/about1.jpg" alt="Premium Quality" style="width: 200px; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <h4>Premium Materials</h4>
                    <p>From sustainable leather to breathable mesh — only the best touches your feet.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="/images/about2.jpg" alt="Iconic Designs" style="width: 200px; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <h4>Designed to Stand Out</h4>
                    <p>Whether minimal or bold, our styles are curated for statement-makers and trendsetters.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="/images/about3.jpg" alt="Community First" style="width: 200px; border-radius: 20px;">
                    <h4>Built Around You</h4>
                    <p>We don’t just make shoes — we build relationships. Your trust means everything.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</main>

<%- include('component/footer') %>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
